org.efs.openreports.objects

Class ORTag

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.efs.openreports.objects.ORTag
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class ORTag
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    The ORTag class is used by OpenReports to assign a tag to an object. Each ORTag instance will have a unique identifier and a String tag and is assigned to the specified objectId and objectClass
